article.headline: Tennessee Tech 76, Bryan 48
article.story: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. -- Daniel Northern had 18 points, nine rebounds and three blocked shots to lead Tennessee Tech to a 76-48 victory over Bryan on Saturday night. Will Barnes had 15 points, while Alex Davis and Kevin Murphy added 10 apiece for the Golden Eagles (1-0), who shot 55 percent from the field (32-for-58). Scott Newton had 21 points and nine rebounds for Bryan. Kyle Terry added 12 points.
